      • getModules

        default Module [] getModules()

      • isBuildProjectOnEmptyModuleList

        default boolean isBuildProjectOnEmptyModuleList()
        Modifies behavior for the case when getModules() returns empty list. By default whole project will be built in this case.
        Returns:
        true if whole project is to be built when no particular module is selected, false effectively skips project compilation
